  "resourceType": "Routine",
  "isPrivate": false,
  "permissions": "{}",
  "isInternal": false,
  "tags": [],
  "versions": [
    {
      "id": "7892456378912345011",
      "publicId": "adapt-teach-v1",
      "versionLabel": "1.0.0",
      "versionNotes": "Initial version of adaptive instructor for personalized learning",
      "isComplete": true,
      "resourceSubType": "RoutineGenerate",
      "config": {
        "__version": "1.0",
        "callDataGenerate": {
          "__version": "1.0",
          "schema": {
            "botStyle": "Educational",
            "maxTokens": 700,
            "temperature": 0.6,
            "prompt": "You are an adaptive learning instructor who personalizes instruction based on student progress.\n\nExercise Results: {{input.exerciseResults}}\nLearning Progress: {{input.learningProgress}}\nLanguage Curricula: {{input.languageCurricula}}\nAssessment Tools: {{input.assessmentTools}}\n\nBased on the learner's performance and progress:\n\n1. **Progress Analysis**: Evaluate their current level and recent performance\n2. **Strengths & Weaknesses**: Identify what they're doing well and areas needing work\n3. **Adaptive Content**: Provide the next lesson/exercise at the appropriate difficulty level\n4. **Learning Strategy**: Suggest personalized learning techniques based on their patterns\n5. **Practice Exercises**: Create 3-5 targeted exercises focusing on weak areas\n6. **Encouragement**: Provide motivating feedback acknowledging their progress\n7. **Next Steps**: Clear path forward with specific goals\n\nAdapt your instruction style to the learner's:\n- Current proficiency level\n- Learning pace\n- Common mistake patterns\n- Preferred learning style (if evident from data)\n\nMake the content engaging and appropriately challenging - not too easy to bore them, not too hard to discourage them.",
            "retryPolicy": {
              "maxAttempts": 2,
              "backoffMultiplier": 1.5,
              "initialDelay": 1000
            }
          }
        },
        "formInput": {
          "__version": "1.0",
          "schema": {
            "containers": [],
            "elements": [
              {
                "fieldName": "exerciseResults",
                "id": "exercise_results_input",
                "label": "Recent Exercise Results",
                "type": "JSON",
                "isRequired": true,
                "props": {
                  "placeholder": "{ \"score\": 85, \"mistakes\": [\"verb conjugation\", \"pronunciation\"], \"timeSpent\": 15 }",
                  "helperText": "Latest exercise performance data"
                }
              },
              {
                "fieldName": "learningProgress",
                "id": "learning_progress_input",
                "label": "Overall Learning Progress",
                "type": "JSON",
                "isRequired": true,
                "props": {
                  "placeholder": "{ \"level\": \"intermediate\", \"completedLessons\": 45, \"totalHours\": 120, \"streakDays\": 15 }",
                  "helperText": "Cumulative learning data"
                }
              },
              {
                "fieldName": "languageCurricula",
                "id": "language_curricula_input",
                "label": "Subject/Language",
                "type": "Text",
                "isRequired": true,
                "props": {
                  "placeholder": "e.g., Spanish, Python Programming, Mathematics",
                  "helperText": "What subject is being learned"
                }
              },
              {
                "fieldName": "assessmentTools",
                "id": "assessment_tools_input",
                "label": "Learning Focus",
                "type": "Selector",
                "isRequired": false,
                "props": {
                  "options": [
                    { "label": "Vocabulary & Grammar", "value": "vocab_grammar" },
                    { "label": "Conversation Skills", "value": "conversation" },
                    { "label": "Written Communication", "value": "writing" },
                    { "label": "Comprehension", "value": "comprehension" },
                    { "label": "Technical Skills", "value": "technical" },
                    { "label": "Problem Solving", "value": "problem_solving" }
                  ],
                  "defaultValue": "vocab_grammar",
                  "helperText": "Primary learning objective"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "formOutput": {
          "__version": "1.0",
          "schema": {
            "containers": [],
            "elements": [
              {
                "fieldName": "adaptiveLesson",
                "id": "adaptive_lesson",
                "label": "Personalized Lesson",
                "type": "Text",
                "isRequired": true,
                "props": {
                  "multiline": true,
                  "minRows": 10
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "executionStrategy": "conversational"
      },
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": "7892456378912345012",
          "language": "en-US",
          "name": "Adaptive Instructor",
          "description": "Provides personalized instruction that adapts to learner progress, creating customized lessons and exercises based on performance data and learning patterns.",
          "instructions": "Provide recent exercise results and overall learning progress. The instructor will analyze performance and deliver personalized content at the appropriate difficulty level."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}